Counting up the sides and diagonals, the sum we want is
\[12AB + 12AC + 12AD + 12AE + 12AF + 6AG.\]We see that $AC = 12,$ $AD = 12 \sqrt{2},$ $AE = 12 \sqrt{3},$ and $AG = 24.$  Also,
\begin{align*}
