&= 12 \cdot 12 + 12 \cdot 12 \sqrt{2} + 12 \cdot 12 \sqrt{3} + 12 \cdot 12 \sqrt{6} + 6 \cdot 24 \\
&= 288 + 144 \sqrt{2} + 144 \sqrt{3} + 144 \sqrt{6}.
\end{align*}Then $a + b + c + d = 288 + 144 + 144 + 144 = \boxed{720}.$

